data.text:
Mumbai, Jul 4 (PTI) Veteran actor Kamal Haasan on Tuesday announced his new film with director H Vinoth, best known for “Theeran Adhigaaram Ondru” and “Valimai”.

The superstar took to Twitter to share the news about his 233rd film.

“And it begins…#RKFI52 #KH233 #RISEtoRULE #HVinoth #Mahendran @RKFI @turmericmediaTM @magizhmandram,” Haasan said in a tweet.

The upcoming film is reportedly a political drama.

It is produced by Haasan and R Mahendran via their Raaj Kamal Films International banner.

The veteran actor recently joined the cast of Nag Ashwin’s multilingual sci-fi movie “Project K”, which stars Prabhas, Deepika Padukone and Amitabh Bachchan. PTI KKP SHD SHD
